### ==========================================
### product-app.http
### Test Categories + Products qua API Gateway
### Lưu ý: Gateway chưa chặn theo role, chỉ yêu cầu AuthGuard (bất kỳ user đăng nhập)
### ==========================================

# Base variables (fallback nếu chưa chọn environment trong http-client.env.json)
@hostname = localhost
@port = 3000
@gateway = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

### Chuẩn bị user đăng nhập để tạo category/product
@prodEmail = prod-{{$timestamp}}@example.com
@prodPassword = Test@123456

### 0) REGISTER
POST {{gateway}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{prodEmail}}",
  "password": "{{prodPassword}}",
  "fullName": "Product Tester"
}

###

### 1) LOGIN
### @name loginProductUser
POST {{gateway}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{prodEmail}}",
  "password": "{{prodPassword}}"
}

###

@prodToken = {{loginProductUser.response.body.accessToken}}

### 2) CATEGORIES - Create
@categorySlug = cat-{{$timestamp}}

### @name createCategory
POST {{gateway}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Category",
  "slug": "{{categorySlug}}",
  "description": "Category created via .http"
}

###

@categoryId = {{createCategory.response.body.id}}

### 3) CATEGORIES - List
GET {{gateway}}/categories?page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 4) CATEGORIES - Get by ID
GET {{gateway}}/categories/{{categoryId}}

###

### 5) CATEGORIES - Get by Slug
GET {{gateway}}/categories/slug/{{categorySlug}}

###

### 6) CATEGORIES - Update
PUT {{gateway}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Category - Updated",
  "description": "Updated by HTTP test"
}

###

### 7) PRODUCTS - Create (priceInt là cents)
@sku = SKU-{{$timestamp}}
@productSlug = product-{{$timestamp}}

### @name createProduct
POST {{gateway}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "{{sku}}",
  "name": "Test Product",
  "slug": "{{productSlug}}",
  "priceInt": 199900,
  "stock": 25,
  "description": "Product created via .http",
  "imageUrls": ["https://example.com/image.jpg"],
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "attributes": { "color": "red", "size": "M" }
}

###

@productId = {{createProduct.response.body.id}}

### 8) PRODUCTS - List + Filters
GET {{gateway}}/products?page=1&pageSize=10&search=Test

###

### 9) PRODUCTS - Get by ID
GET {{gateway}}/products/{{productId}}

###

### 10) PRODUCTS - Get by Slug
GET {{gateway}}/products/slug/{{productSlug}}

###

### 11) PRODUCTS - Update
PUT {{gateway}}/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priceInt": 179900,
  "stock": 30,
  "description": "Updated via .http"
}

###

### 12) PRODUCTS - Delete (tuỳ chọn)
# DELETE {{gateway}}/products/{{productId}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}

###